Notes
---------------------------------


Credits
---------------------------------
CMS uses the smarty template engine in various places.  Their license and 
various documentation files are located in the smarty subdirectory of this 
distribution.  Their website is located at: http://smarty.php.net

CMS uses HTMLArea 3.0 as it's content WYSIWYG.  HTMLArea is released under 
the htmlArea license (based on the BSD license) and is located at: 
http://www.interactivetools.com/products/htmlarea/

CMS uses the phplayers dhtml menu.  PHPLayers is released under the LGPL
license and is located at: http://phplayersmenu.sourceforge.net/

CMS uses the XML-RPC library written by Keith Devens.  It is released under
the Artistic license and can be found at:
http://keithdevens.com/software/xmlrpc
